### MongoDB Emails Endpoints
# These endpoints provide paginated access to emails with various filters

# --- Variables ---
@host = http://localhost:8000
@api_key = your_api_key_here
@auth_token = Bearer {{api_key}}

### Get Recent Emails (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/recent?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Recent Emails (Page 2)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/recent?page=2
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Oldest Emails (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/oldest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Successful Emails (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/successful?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Failed Emails (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/failed?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Pending Emails (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/pending?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails by Category - Sent (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/by-category?category=sent&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails by Category - Received (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/by-category?category=received&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails by Category - Failed (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/by-category?category=failed&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails by Category - Queued (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/by-category?category=queued&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails by Category - Processing (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/by-category?category=processing&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails by Direction - Inbound (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/by-direction?direction=inbound&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails by Direction - Outbound (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/by-direction?direction=outbound&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Emails with Attachments (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/with-attachments?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Processed Emails (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/processed?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Email by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/email_id_here
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Sample Email ID lookup
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/emails/67890abcdef1234567890abc
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
